<bibRefCitation id="9035D68AFFC8FFF4E5B3AA55FF63FAF3" author="Fedotova, Z. A. &amp; Sidorenko, V. S." pageId="1" pageNumber="24" pagination="235 - 277" refId="ref4217" refString="Fedotova, Z. A., Sidorenko, V. S. 2007. New taxa of gall midges (Diptera, Cecidomyiidae, Porricondylinae) with reduced wing venation and flagellomeres from Russia. An International Journal of Dipterological Research, 18 (4), 235 - 277." type="journal article" year="2007">Fedotova et Sidorenko, 2007</bibRefCitation>
